         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">His Majesty the King ¶ of Bavaria ¶ has most graciously deigned, according to the sovereign decree of 14th of January of this year, to confer on the Head of the botanic Institute in Melbourne, Profess...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">74.01.28a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Adolph von Pfretzschner</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS, MS M200a.16, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS is a printed certificate with a decorated upper border and additional similar decoration around the 'Brevet' in the lower left corner. M's name and details and the name of the Order to which he was being admitted have been entered by hand.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Seine Majestaet der Koenig</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">von Bayern</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">haben Sich vermöge allerhöchster Entschliessung vom 14ten Januar laufd. Jahres allergnädigst bewogen gefunden, dem</seg> Vorstand der botanischen Anstalt in Melbourne, Professor Baron Müller, das Ritterkreuz 1ter Klasse <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">des Königlichen Verdienst Ordens vom heiligen Michael zu verleihen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Zur Legitimation hierüber wird gegenwärtiges Brevèt von dem Staats-Ministerium des Königlichen Hauses und des Aeusern, als Grosskanzler-Amte des erwähnten Ordens, ausgestellt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">München den</seg> 28ten Januar 1874.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>v. Pfretzschner<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Ministry's seal is affixed to the certificate, next to von Pfretzschner's signature.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Brevet</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">für den</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Vorstand der botanischen Anstalt </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">in Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Professor Baron Müller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Die allergnädigste Verleihung des Ritterkreuzes 1. Klasse des Königlichen Verdienst-Ordens vom heiligen Michael betreffend.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">[De Kentele]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">His Majesty the King</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">of Bavaria</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">has most graciously deigned, according to the sovereign decree of 14th of January of this year, to confer on the Head of the botanic Institute in Melbourne, Professor Baron von Mueller, the Knight's Cross Ist Class of the Royal Order of Merit of Saint Michael.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In legitimation of this the present certificate is issued by the Ministry of State of the Royal House and of Foreign Affairs, as office of the Grand Chancellor of the said Order.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Munich, 28 January 1874.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>von Pfretzschner.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Certificate</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">for the</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Head of the botanic Institute</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">in Melbourne,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Professor Baron von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Re: The most gracious conferment of the Knight's Cross 1. Class of the Royal Order of Merit of Saint Michael.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">[De Kentele]</p>
         </div>
      </body>
